{"tid":2201661,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"有個IG 畫家抄宮崎駿筆下KiKi 扮原創搵錢，仲要勁多支持原創嘅文青推崇","createTime":"2020-09-14T03:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T14:50:28.000Z","uid":357083,"like":36,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a1e93c48bde59111f03146f1ad76c3544e9da3","tid":2201661,"uid":357083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"一開始幾鍾意@Peep_projects 依種畫風所以follow<br />\n之後佢開始喺大南街開畫展<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppq2Xam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fppq2Xam.jpg&h=60f9a26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwdLUVw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwdLUVw.jpg&h=4169e9a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個主題叫KiKi x KiKi <br />\n仲講到明係用魔女宅急便做靈感<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXunW84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXunW84.jpg&h=cea10525&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NayDvvf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNayDvvf.jpg&h=bde122c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無知嘅我一開始都話，噢，幾靚wor<br />\n但之後我啲讀art ge friend 同我講<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n吓，其實佢咁用人地個牌子，就算佢二次都好，咁樣賣print 同出商品都係抄襲同侵權。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗一諗，係wor，就算係cotton on, topshop， 佢地出Disney theme/Friends theme ge T-shirt, 都要買左版權先可以出，出嘅tee 都會有依啲牌子嘅logo 喺個tag 度。<br />\n<br />\n喂，咁，真係好過份喎。<br />\n仲要成班深水埗文青去支持，<span class=\"x-large\">講支持創作，但其實係支持緊抄襲者。</span><br />\n<br />\n而我想講，佢黎緊又黎料，今次抄 L&eacute;on: The Professional (這個殺手不太冷）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sass8jr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsass8jr.jpg&h=78dd1970&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9b477006c37fd297672c163eaa8ba14e8e9d42f","tid":2201661,"uid":45431,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"有無fc過佢有無傾版權？"},{"pid":"a02511e033fef10d3c2075c4f1edbd9dae